:::'''Verdant Manager:''' Tweet tweet! It's dangerous ahead. Unauthorized personnel are prohibited from entering, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What is this place?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030803-->
